<body>
    <h1>✨ Wake the Week</h1>
    <p>A simple, effortless space to plan your week — set goals, track daily habits, and plan weekends with ease.</p>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>📧 Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions, feedback, or need help with the app, feel free to reach out:<br>
        <strong><a href="mailto:waketheweek@outlook.com">waketheweek@outlook.com</a></strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>📖 FAQ</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>How do I add a weekly goal?</strong> Tap the <code>+</code> button in the Goals section, enter your goal, and save.</li>
            <li><strong>Will my data be lost if I reinstall the app?</strong> Data is stored locally on your device. To back it up, enable <strong>iCloud Sync</strong> in Preferences.</li>
            <li><strong>How do I unlock themes?</strong> Visit the Vibe Shop, pick a theme, and unlock it by watching an ad or purchasing the Ad-Free version.</li>
            <li><strong>What does Ad-Free include?</strong> Unlimited entries across all sections, all themes unlocked, and no ads.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <hr>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2026 Wake the Week</p>
    </div>
